Example Usage¶

import cirq
import qbraid

# Create a cirq circuit
q0, q1 = [cirq.LineQubit(i) for i in range(2)]
cirq_circuit = cirq.Circuit(cirq.H(q0), cirq.CNOT(q0, q1))

# Run circuit on any supported device using the qraid device wrapper
qbraid_device = qbraid.device_wrapper("AerSimulator", "IBM")
qbraid_job = qbraid_device.run(cirq_circuit)  # run cirq circuit on IBM Aer simulator
qbraid_result = qbraid_job.result
print(qbraid_result.data)  # view the raw data from the run
...

Devices API¶

DeviceLikeWrapper(name, provider[, vendor])

Abstract interface for device-like classes.

JobLikeWrapper(device, vendor_jlo)

Abstract interface for job-like classes.

ResultWrapper(vendor_rlo)

Abstract interface for result-like classes.

get_devices([provider, vendor, simulator, creds])

Prints all available devices, tabulated by provider and vendor.

update_config(vendor)

Update the config associated with given vendor

DeviceError(*message)

Base class for errors raised while processing a device.

JobError(*message)

Base class for errors raised by Jobs.

ConfigError(*message)

Base class for errors raised while setting a user configuartion

AWS Devices Interface (qbraid.devices.aws)¶

This module contains the classes used to run quantum circuits on devices available through AWS.

BraketDeviceWrapper(name, provider, **fields)

Wrapper class for Amazon Braket Device objects.

BraketQuantumTaskWrapper(device, quantum_task)

Wrapper class for Amazon Braket QuantumTask objects.

BraketGateModelResultWrapper(gate_model_result)

Wrapper class for Amazon Braket GateModelQuantumTaskResult objects.

Google Devices Interface (qbraid.devices.google)¶

This module contains the classes used to run quantum circuits on devices available through Google.

CirqEngineWrapper(name, provider, **fields)

Wrapper class for Google Cirq Engine objects.

CirqSimulatorWrapper(name, provider, **fields)

Wrapper class for Google Cirq Simulator objects.

CirqEngineJobWrapper(device, vendor_jlo)

Wrapper class for Google Cirq EngineJob objects.

CirqResultWrapper(cirq_result)

Cirq Result wrapper class.

IBM Devices Interface (qbraid.devices.ibm)¶

This module contains the classes used to run quantum circuits on devices available through IBM.

QiskitBackendWrapper(name, provider, **fields)

Wrapper class for IBM Qiskit Backend objects.

QiskitJobWrapper(device, vendor_jlo)

Wrapper class for IBM Qiskit Job objects.

QiskitResultWrapper(vendor_rlo)

Qiskit Result wrapper class.
